USERS:

User – Answers questions and views personality prediction.
Admin (optional) – Manages dataset, model updates, and system maintenance.

MODULES:

User Registration/Login (optional)
Questionnaire Module – Displays personality questions.
Response Collection Module – Stores user answers.
Data Preprocessing Module – Cleans and prepares data.
ML Prediction Module – Predicts personality type.
Result Display Module – Shows predicted personality and description.
Admin Module (optional) – Manage data and model.
